  "merge_notes": "School conflict: 2 ICT, 1 SMC, 1 SMC (Smart Money Concepts). Picked ICT by majority. The 'Daily Profiles' project defines premium in the context of Seek and Destroy (consolidation) for mean-reversion, while ICT and SMC projects emphasize trend-following shorts in bearish bias. The unified card incorporates both contexts: premium as a sell zone in bearish bias or consolidation, with special note that in consolidation, fading back to equilibrium is the primary trade.",
